<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../../partials/head') %>
<body class="bg-[#0F172A] text-slate-200 min-h-screen flex font-sans">
    <%- include('../../partials/sidebar') %>
    <main class="ml-64 flex-1 p-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Mastering Ideate</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">From a rough sketch to a community-backed project.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mb-6">1</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Draft & Post</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">Don't wait for perfection. Use a catchy title. Upload sketches or diagrams to explain better. Select the right category (Tech, Social, etc.).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mb-6">2</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Engage</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">Reply to comments. People who comment are your potential co-founders or first users. Value their input, even if it's critical.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mb-6">3</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Iterate</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">Use the "Edit" feature to update your idea description based on feedback. Show the community that the idea is evolving.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ri-flashlight-fill text-yellow-400"></i> Pro Tips for Visibility</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-blue-500 text-xl mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Use Visuals</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Ideas with images get 3x more engagement than text-only posts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-blue-500 text-xl mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Ask Questions</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">End your description with a specific question like "Would you pay $5 for this?" to trigger discussion.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-blue-500 text-xl mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Complete Profile</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Users trust ideas from profiles with a photo and bio. It shows you are real.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-blue-500 text-xl mt-1"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Share Externally</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Copy your post link and share it on Twitter/LinkedIn to bring outside traffic.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
</body>
</html>